CHANGELOG of ChemSpot
----------------------

1.5 - 2013-04-02
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improved annotation merging component
- Improved performance of tagging document collections
- Slightly reduced memory consumption and fixed a memory leak
- Adapted output format to print all identifiers instead of just one
- Made all formerly mandatory parameters optional
- Several bugfixes and minor improvements


1.4.2 - 2013-02-20
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
- Added new parameter -f for reading a collection of text files
- Bugfixes


1.4.1 - 2013-01-23
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
- Optimized parameter evaluation code


1.4 - 2012-11-15
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improved match expansion.
- Improved recognition of multi-token entities.
- Improved recognition of plural forms.
- Sanitized application parameter settings.
- Several bug fixes and minor improvements.



1.3 - 2012-10-08
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
- New tagger component for chemical formulae.
- Integrated ABBREV tagger for recognition of biochemical abbreviations 
  by Schwartz et al.
- Added multi-threading functionality.
- Improved normalization.
- Made ChemSpot code compliant with Java version 1.6.
- Code refactoring and bug fixes.
